      {
        "id": 6906,
        "title": "Valores de variables",
        "type": "practiceLevel1",
        "lessons": [
          {
            "title": "Using numbers",
            "id": 59673,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Los nombres de las variables pueden contener <strong>números</strong> también. Agregar números es útil con múltiples variables similares. Vamos a crear la variable <code>car1</code> aquí.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" car1\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"6\" endIndex=\"10\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"1 car\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>car1</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Giving a variable a value",
            "id": 59676,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Después de crear y nombrar una variable, usamos el signo <code>=</code> para almacenar un <strong>valor</strong> dentro de ella. Como <code>const city = \"Chicago\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" city = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Chicago&quot;\" class=\"string\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"11\" endIndex=\"12\" /><option startIndex=\"13\" endIndex=\"22\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>=</code> seguido de <code>\"Chicago\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Completing your first variable",
            "id": 59675,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para terminar de crear una variable, ponemos un punto y coma, <code>;</code>, al final de la línea.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" city = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Chicago&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"22\" endIndex=\"23\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\".\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "String",
            "id": 59720,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Los valores que hemos estado almacenando como <code>\"Chicago\"</code> son <strong>strings</strong>. Los strings son palabras entre comillas dobles.</p><code version=\"2\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\" codelang=\"javascript\"><content><text value=\"&quot;Chicago&quot;\" class=\"string\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"1\" /><option startIndex=\"8\" endIndex=\"9\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"'\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"'\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>\"</code> seguido de <code>\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Sentence",
            "id": 59714,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Las cadenas pueden contener todo tipo de letras y símbolos, incluidos espacios. Por ejemplo, <code>\"Winter is coming.\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\" codelang=\"javascript\"><content><text value=\"&quot;Winter is coming.&quot;\" class=\"string\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"1\" /><option startIndex=\"1\" endIndex=\"18\" /><option startIndex=\"18\" endIndex=\"19\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>\"</code> seguido de <code>Winter is coming.</code> y finalmente <code>\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question 1",
            "id": 59742,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Cuál es el valor de esta variable?</p><code version=\"2\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\" codelang=\"javascript\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" name = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Karin&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /></content></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>\"Karin\"</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>name</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>\"Karin\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question 2",
            "id": 59772,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Cómo sabemos que un valor es una cadena?</p><selection multiple=\"multiple\"><item correct=\"true\" value=\"1\">Es una palabra entre comillas dobles</item><item correct=\"false\" value=\"2\">Contiene un signo <code>=</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Es una palabra entre comillas dobles.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question 3",
            "id": 59690,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Qué está pasando en este código?</p><code version=\"2\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\" codelang=\"javascript\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" browser = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Chrome&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /></content></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">La variable <code>browser</code> almacena el valor <code>\"Chrome\"</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">La variable <code>\"Chrome\"</code> almacena el valor <code>browser</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">La variable <code>browser</code> almacena el valor <code>\"Chrome\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question 4",
            "id": 59743,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Cuál es el nombre de esta variable?</p><code version=\"2\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\" codelang=\"javascript\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" hobby = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Tree shaping&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /></content></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>hobby</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>\"Tree shaping\"</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>hobby</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example 1",
            "id": 59691,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Crea una variable <code>job</code> y asígnale el valor <code>\"Plumber\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\" codelang=\"javascript\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" name = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Mario&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" job = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Plumber&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"20\" endIndex=\"27\" /><option startIndex=\"28\" endIndex=\"29\" /><option startIndex=\"30\" endIndex=\"39\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>let job</code> seguido de <code>=</code> y finalmente <code>\"Plumber\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example 2",
            "id": 59745,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Crea una variable <code>company</code> y asígnale un valor de cadena.</p><code version=\"2\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\" codelang=\"javascript\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" company = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Apple&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"11\" /><option startIndex=\"12\" endIndex=\"13\" /><option startIndex=\"14\" endIndex=\"21\" /><option startIndex=\"21\" endIndex=\"22\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"Apple\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>let company</code> seguido de <code>=</code> y luego <code>\"Apple\"</code>, <code>;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example 3",
            "id": 59747,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Asigna a la variable <code>island</code> un valor de tipo string.</p><code version=\"2\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\" codelang=\"javascript\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" island = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Malta&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"15\" endIndex=\"16\" /><option startIndex=\"16\" endIndex=\"21\" /><option startIndex=\"21\" endIndex=\"22\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"'\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"'\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>\"</code> seguido de <code>Malta</code> y finalmente <code>\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example 4",
            "id": 59746,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Asigna a la variable <code>device</code> el valor de cadena <code>\"Desktop\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\" codelang=\"javascript\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" device = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Desktop&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"15\" endIndex=\"24\" /></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>\"Desktop\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          }
        ]
